```{r pancreas 32723384, include=FALSE}

PMID_32723384 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32723384', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32723384 <- paste0(PMID_32723384$journal,' ', PMID_32723384$year, ' ', PMID_32723384$month,';', PMID_32723384$volume,'(', PMID_32723384$number,'):', PMID_32723384$pages)

PubMed_32723384 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32723384$eprint)

doi_32723384 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32723384$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
